    "Description": "Mechanical Fidget Alphabet, Numbers, and Glyphs A minimalist mechanical-keycap–inspired fidget design featuring customizable letters, numbers, and symbols. Each key is designed with smooth edges and balanced proportions for a clean, premium look that prints reliably on FDM printers. This model is fully customizable in Bambu Studio , allowing you to easily adjust the font style and text size to create personalized initials, words, or symbols. Perfect for keychains, desk fidgets, name tags, or small custom gifts. Designed with simplicity and printability in mind, making it suitable for beginners while still offering creative freedom for advanced users. Features: Mechanical keycap–inspired design Supports alphabet, numbers, and glyphs Font and text size adjustable in Bambu Studio Clean geometry for smooth printing Ideal for keychains, fidgets, and personalization projects A simple, elegant model made for customization and everyday use.",
